      },
      "lineNbr": 785,
      "author": {
        "id": 1000898
      },
      "writtenOn": "2014-08-14T22:01:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "you need to set the function pointers to the new (static) functions you defined in this file. This is similar to enc_sse2.c:968 for instance:\n\nVP8SSE4x4 \u003d SSE4x4;\nVP8SSE8x8 \u003d SSE8x8;\n\netc.",
      "revId": "a7dd7d4c3412ed314abe4709e11c7bff3f86bfae",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
